966410fab233d44d4381036b0a2eb92a51f19067252" style=3D"color:#d40000;text-de=
coration:none;font-weight:bold" class=3D"sdf">seething at her</a></u>. <br/=
><br/>Whether that was or still is true at this hour, I don=E2=80=99t know.=
 But I will say this: Nancy Pelosi worked closely with Joe Biden for a very=
 long time; they accomplished a great deal together. She respects him. She =
feels for him. She loves him. But, in the end, she put all of that aside to=
 do what she thought was
necessary for Democrats to have any chance of preventing Donald Trump from =
retaking the White House. One dearly hopes that, in the fullness of time, B=
iden will come to see Pelosi=E2=80=99s actions through that prism and not a=
s a personal betrayal, and that whatever damage has been done to their rela=
